<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1004613">PC鬼——桃大将<br>“欧嘞，三舅”<br>“哈，自我介绍，事先声明，本大爷从最初开始就是climax的！”<br>“看在桃子布丁的份上，我就给你展示一下童绊镇最强之鬼的全部实力。”<br>“啊咧，你对打架，不感兴趣？”<br>“谁是笨蛋啊，你这家伙！”<br>“喂喂喂，谁把狗带过来的，吉娃娃也不行，狗狗不要靠近本大爷啊~~~~！”（跑开）<br><strong>设定：</strong>真身如同传说中的赤鬼一般面色通红长有双角<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><img src="http://m.qpic.cn/psb?/V14CC14a2xAKF0/C9UibV47pmOIqs735LmMmGe4io1a*UxjCm5KtYvdFAc!/b/dLYAAAAAAAAA&amp;bo=agH9AAAAAAADB7Q!&amp;rf=viewer_4" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></div></div></div>人类形象则是黑发红瞳，穿着皮衣牛仔裤，腰带上还挂着铁链，一句话来概括，便是从外观到内里都非常凶悍的18岁青年。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0p